Dialogs.Dialog: How are you going to take the photo today?
Am I right like this? Please teach me properly.
Should I not be looking at the camera?
Good work. Did you take a lot?
Fufu, you were taking pictures with enthusiasm.
I took quite a lot of pictures without realizing it...
That's right. I took a lot of photos today...
I want to keep a lot of your photos,▲高嶺＊＊▲.
I got a lot of photos, and I'm happy.
You took a lot of photos. I was surprised.
You took a lot of photos, why don't we finish for today?
Hmm, right. Let's finish for today.
Didn't you take a little too much?
Oh, I guess I'm getting on with it a little bit, right?
Uh... It's been a long time.
Yes... It seems a took a lot of photos without realizing it.
I wish I could take a good picture.
Did you get a good picture?
It's just a pleasure to take them.
Ah... I'm sorry, I didn't notice.

Oh, are you tired? I'm sorry.

Haha, you pushed it to the limit.
Couldn't you take a good photo?

I'm going to get angry if you continue.
I'd be happy if you could take a beautiful picture.
Now that we're here, let's take a good picture.
Will the next one be in the album?
Take a lot of pictures and have a lot of memories.
I'm wondering what kind of photo it will be...
Let's cherish our memories one by one.
The figure of you holding the camera is also one of my memories... I'm kidding.
I want to keep a lot of memories.
Is this also a memory of us?
This pose... I can't seem to do it...
Don't look too much... It's impossible to say it...
I want you to take beautiful pictures... but...
Is this fine? Is this good?
Emm, excuse me, shouldn't I move?
Kya~. Did you take it now?

Alright, I'll make it a good one!

I want to take a good look...
It's cute no matter where you look!

I should give it a try...

Did you feel a little too relaxed?
You can take a lot of pictures♪
I wonder if it's a little embarrassing...
It's difficult to make it natural.

Ah! Emm... I'm worried about the wind...
No... don't look at me so weird.
Oh, what are you looking at?
Stop it. Geez... I'll get angry okay?
No... It's embarrassing to be seen from behind, isn't it?
Are you trying to take a funny photo?
Yah... Huh? Where did the wind come from?
Ah, right now... you're not shooting, right?
Ah! I don't like it now.
I don't want to shoot that kind of thing.
Emm... geez. You can't do that next time, okay?
Oh, I'm going to take a picture of that.
Why do you want to take pictures of that?
Hey, what are you shooting now?
I wonder what I should do.
